                      continuations. This was perhaps the best presentation I
                      saw at the conference and it was on something weâ€™ll
                      definitely be using.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      TheÂ <a
                        href="ftp://ftp.cs.kun.nl/pub/Clean/papers/2006/plar2006-FLOPS06-iDataForTheWeb.pdf"
                        >iData toolkit</a
                      >Â is aÂ <a href="http://clean.cs.ru.nl/">Clean</a>Â library
